title: How-To: Make Ovenly's Pumpkin Pie with Toasted Marshmallow Cinnamon Fluff
description:
This year, give the classic Turkey Day dessert an update with toasted marshmallow cinnamon fluff. CINNAMON. FLUFF. The genius recipe comes from Erin Patinkin and Agatha Kulaga of Ovenly in Brooklyn, NY.

You might want to skip the poultry and potatoes and dig right into this ooey gooey masterpiece.

Check out the recipe here: https://munchies.vice.com/en_us/article/d7kqxy/pumpkin-pie-cinnamon-fluff
